{"tid":1107001,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"講廣東話就係香港本土電影?","createTime":"2019-04-15T02:42:16.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-15T02:57:01.000Z","uid":33668,"like":2,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"ef123e24ca7d7ad1cd9e514ae65af9832128ad59","tid":1107001,"uid":33668,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-15T02:42:16.000Z","msg":"近年有一個諗法 我一直都諗唔通<br />\n<br />\n到底香港本土電影係咪一定要講廣東話?<br />\n<br />\n我認為電影唔應該受語言所限 香港人拍 就算係講英文 講虫語 都可以係好電影<br />\n<br />\n相反講廣東話嘅奶共電影都唔算本土電影<br />\n<br />\n點解提出呢個諗法 係因為怕兩樣嘢<br />\n<br />\n1) 當局 (我都唔知指邊一批人好)偷借廣東話同化大灣圈電影及娛樂事業<br />\n- 例如近呢1-2年會用大灣區電影 唔再講香港電影<br />\n- 港產片會慢慢偷換慨念變廣產片 (因為廣東話...然後又慢慢偷換為廣東電影)<br />\n- 利好因素係稅務問題令香港制作人及明星抱觀望態度 (但其實近年不斷將香港3-4線 搬去大陸用大陸方法&quot;打造&quot;變紅星 就係實驗香港人材斷層等相關問題)<br />\n<br />\n2) 香港優勢之一係國際語言 三文兩語 其實係大陸最忌諱嘅對外對內的宣傳媒介 大家最愛的港式電視劇 綜藝 都已經幾腳工夫就打殘哂 電影及歌曲係未死得哂的領域 應串&quot;土&quot;必爭"},{"pid":"9f5241fa371c956cd468227cb11c04ca4f974278","tid":1107001,"uid":196924,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-15T02:42:47.000Z","msg":"三文兩語<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b63e5362f27102f1c8cbebcdd0919d413c26de22","tid":1107001,"uid":99607,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-15T02:49:51.000Z","msg":"本土電影意思係港產片 香港出產的電影"},{"pid":"0d9cebd6bffb4b1a30c00c6e755a5d2fcd60cb7e","tid":1107001,"uid":33668,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"b63e5362f27102f1c8cbebcdd0919d413c26de22","tid":1107001,"uid":99607,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-15T02:49:51.000Z","msg":"本土電影意思係港產片 香港出產的電影"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-15T02:54:03.000Z","msg":"我都認同<br />\n其實我都係用緊消去法 搵返所謂本土電影的本質 想宣揚點先係港產片 又或者本土主義底下應支持邊一種電影<br />\n支持香港電影=支持港產片?<br />\n支持廣東話=支持港產片?<br />\n好似都唔係必然"},{"pid":"bfc4657670d168487fe78d47d40e12f36582b670","tid":1107001,"uid":33668,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"9f5241fa371c956cd468227cb11c04ca4f974278","tid":1107001,"uid":196924,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-15T02:42:47.000Z","msg":"三文兩語<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-15T02:57:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />第一個留言的重要性"}]}